---
import Container from "../ui/Container.astro";
import SectionHeader from "../ui/SectionHeader.astro";
---

<section class="story">

  <Container>

    <div class="story-grid">

      <div class="heading">

        <SectionHeader
          eyebrow="OUR STORY"
          title="A Legacy Built on Trust, Strengthened Through Generations"
        />

      </div>

      <div class="content">

        <p>
          <strong>S R Group</strong> is a family-owned chemical manufacturing
          group based in <strong>Chhatral GIDC, Gujarat</strong>.
        </p>

        <p>
          Established in <strong>1997</strong> by the late
          <strong>Shri Ramanbhai Patel</strong> together with his sons,
          <strong>Nilesh Patel</strong> and
          <strong>Krushi Patel</strong>, the company was founded with a clear
          vision—to build a business rooted in integrity, dependable products,
          and lasting customer relationships.
        </p>

        <p>
          Over the years, S R Group has grown into three manufacturing
          companies —
          <strong>S R Industries</strong>,
          <strong>S R Plast</strong> and
          <strong>S R Polymers</strong> — manufacturing industrial chemicals,
          distilled solvents and unsaturated polyester resins for customers
          across India while steadily expanding into international markets.
        </p>

        <p>
          With a strong foundation built over nearly three decades,
          <strong>Henil Patel</strong> and
          <strong>Kushal Patel</strong> represent the next generation of
          S R Group, carrying forward its legacy by combining the company's
          core values with a modern approach to manufacturing, innovation
          and long-term business relationships.
        </p>

        <p>
          As the business continues to evolve, the principles on which it was
          founded remain unchanged—manufacturing dependable products, honouring
          commitments and building partnerships that stand the test of time.
        </p>

      </div>

    </div>

  </Container>

</section>

<style>

.story{
padding:7rem 0;
}

.story-grid{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:1fr 1.45fr;
gap:6rem;
align-items:start;
}

.heading{
position:sticky;
top:7rem;
}

.content{
display:flex;
flex-direction:column;
gap:2rem;
}

.content p{
margin:0;
font-size:1.08rem;
line-height:2;
color:var(--color-text-light);
}

.content strong{
color:var(--color-primary);
font-weight:600;
}

@media (max-width:900px){

.story{
padding:5rem 0;
}

.story-grid{
grid-template-columns:1fr;
gap:3rem;
}

.heading{
position:static;
}

}

</style>
